This is a simple route calculator for fetching routes between point A and B with option for traveling via point C.
The starting point is either custom location or the geolocation of the user.
The transport mode is custom: user can pick car, bicycle or pedestrian mode.
The app also checks the weather forecast both in the starting end ending point( based on the hour of arrival/departure).
The app gives the user written instructions on how to arrive from point A to point B.
The history of the searches is saved in database and can be browse at any moment.
The app has different interface for mobile/desktop.

